To remove this constraint, pass in `:must-exists nil'.  E.g.

\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/aoeu\"\)                                        â‡’ t
\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/aoeu:10\"\)                                     â‡’ t
\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/aoeu:/hello world/\"\)                          â‡’ t
\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/non-existent\"\)                                â‡’ nil
\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/non-existent\" :must-exists nil\)               â‡’ t
\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/non-existent:10\" :must-exists nil\)            â‡’ t
\(~file-pattern? \"/tmp/non-existent:/hello world/\" :must-exists nil\) â‡’ t
"
