started, change the directory."
  (interactive "DDirectory: ")
  (cond
   ((get-buffer "*eshell*")
    (with-current-buffer "*eshell*"
      (cd dir)
      (eshell-emit-prompt))
    (switch-to-buffer "*eshell*"))
   (t
    (cd dir)
    (eshell))))

